text: A must visit place for vegetarian food with authentic Indian flavours. They serve breakfast, lunch and dinner...dine in and take away..budget friendly and so much delicious food.

If you live far from little india and are debating going to this branch, please do go. The idli were perfect, dosa could’ve been better and vada’s were not fresh. But overall including chutneys and sambar, it was decent. Not comparable to the main one in little india but this is the best in this area! Highly recommend!
Good quality and fresh food. Very fast service. The ghee roast dosa, vada etc are really good with different chutneys.
Hot vegetarian vegan food. No need go Little India. I repeat customer
A friend recommended their Nasi Briyani n I'd gone back twice.  I'll try other items next time.  The coffee shop was a little crowded w stuff of stall sellers. Thus, no atmosphere lah.
